<HEADLINE> Nielsen Considers 'Titanic' Spoof </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Leslie Nielsen's career blossomed with spoofs  
like ``Naked Gun'' and the upcoming ``The Big Bang,'' a send-up of 
space movies. 
</P>
<P>
	Now he's dreaming of another target.  
</P>
<P>
	``If anything is spoofable, it would be `Titanic' because there  
must be very few people in the world who have not seen the film,'' 
he said in a recent interview. 
</P>
<P>
	``It would have been very ripe for it, but at the moment there's  
nothing cooking in that area,'' Nielsen added. 
</P>
<P>
	The 77-year-old actor's space spoof is due out next year.  
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
